\newlabel{fig:tumor_growth}{{10.10}{64}{Detailed tumor growth analysis showing progression patterns under different treatment modalities. The analysis reveals distinct growth kinetics and sex differences in growth trajectories under hormonal influence}{figure.caption.55}{}}
